description: a simple shopping list application This is the a simple Android application serving the purpose of a shopping list. I modelled it after how I would use a piece of paper and kept it as simple as possible. Core features: * Simple and intuitive to use * Dark and Light user interface mode * No permissions required * No tracking or sharing any data * No ads Languages: * Azerbaijani * Bengali * Czech * English * Finnish * French * Georgian * German * Hebrew * Italian * Lithuanian * Norwegian Bokmal * Polish * Portuguese * Russian * Turkish * Ukrainian
